title: This Speaker Has A Special Trick...
description: (   ) --- Today's Mystery Video -  Boombotix Speaker (USA Link) -  Boombotix Speaker (International) -   This speaker is a combination of a portable unit and a subwoofer attachment / charge dock. The Boombotix is also rugged an water resistant.  From the manufacturer -   On its own the Boombot Pro+ is a wireless speaker that gives you premium audio anytime, anywhere. When it is seamlessly docked on the BASS Station, the combination of the two units form a powerful system that will turn heads. The Boombot BASS Station consists of two speakers that work in harmony to create a unique blend of an ultra-portable speaker that can instantly become an enhanced home audio experience. The updated version of the Boombot PRO+ features a wireless rapid-charging system. When docked on the BASS Station, the Boombot PRO+ charges 50% faster than standard USB charging.
